The Gauteng Department of Education intends to convert 4 Public Ordinary Schools to Schools of Specialisation. This establishment will be in the best interest of Education as these schools will be:  The Gauteng Department of Education invites the community and interested parties to submit representations regarding the proposed conversion of the schools within 90 days from the date of publication to: Ms. Mmule Madonsela Director: Public Ordinary Schools 3rd Floor, 17 Simmonds Street Johannesburg 2001   